<p>LiveCode</p>
<p></p>
<p>by RunRev</p>
<p></p>
<p>LiveCode is the open source app creation platform that empowers everyone to create apps.</p>
<p></p>
<p>It provides the easiest path to coding and app creation for those starting out, learning to program or creating their first app. For experienced professionals, LiveCode is the fastest route to creating your next #1 app, utility or powerful new business system.</p>
<p></p>
<p>LiveCode lets you:</p>
<p>- Create your user interface by drag dropping objects onto a canvas</p>
<p>- Use an English-like language to add logic to your app</p>
<p>- Include graphics, multimedia or animation</p>
<p>- Process text and data using natural language</p>
<p>- Edit your app while it is running live</p>
<p>- Write your app once then deploy it to iOS, Android, Windows, Mac or Linux</p>
<p>- Create server applications using the same language</p>
<p></p>
<p>Founded in 1997, RunRev are the makers of LiveCode. LiveCode was formerly known as Revolution. RunRev is based in Edinburgh, Scotland.</p>
<p></p>
<p>For more information, please visit us on the Web at:</p>
<p></p>
<p>http://www.runrev.com</p>
<p></p>
<p>You can contact us at support@runrev.com</p>
<p></p>
<p>RunRev is a trading name of Runtime Revolution Ltd, a private limited company SC200728. LiveCode is copyright 2000-13, Runtime Revolution Ltd. All trademarks are the property of their respective owners.</p>
